data.description: 4 Bedroom home with a NEW 2023 ROOF situated to St. Lucie County's Ski Lake!  Pack your kayak, paddleboard and skiis to enjoy the water activities with your neighbors or enjoy the sunset in peace on your very own dock. No HOA so you can build the backyard of your dreams with a fire pit, fence, out door summer kitchen, etc. This turnkey home has has several features: remodeled bathrooms, a split foor plan, vaulted ceilings, tile throughout and shutters.  Conveniently located just minutes from Tradition, shopping, dining, Cleveland Clinic and I-95 highway access. Schedule your showing today! Whether you're seeking a permanent residence, a vacation retreat, or an investment opportunity, this property has it all.
